location.fullValue: The Sable Plan, Glacier Creek Townhomes

data.description:
Beautifully updated home in Lakeville with one of the largest yards in the area!  Turn-key and move in ready! Gorgeous updated kitchen with stainless steel appliances.   Large family room downstairs, huge Patio for entertaining and Partial privacy fence and on a corner lot.   Close to restaurants and city park just 1 block away.  Farmington schools.  Wonderful layout - seems bigger than it is – Come and See! 

2014 - new Roof, windows, gutters and shed.
2015 - new furnace, washing machine.  
2018 - new microwave, oven & downstairs flooring.
2019 - new fence & dryer.
2020 - new upstairs carpet, triple osmosis water. purifier, black top to left side of garage & blinds.
2021 - new patio.

Book a showing today because at this price point this amazing home will not last long!!!
